p: The median age was 29 years (interquartile range (IQR) 24–37), and 72% (67) were female. The median CD4 cell count and viral load were 550 cells/μL (IQR 387–698) and 4.68 log 10 copies/mL (IQR 4.13–5.21), respectively. Median viral load for persons with AHI was 6.18 log 10 copies/mL (IQR 5.89–7.00).
